<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ru">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>{{.Title}} — RepricerX</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
  <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%" style="margin-bottom: 16px;">
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 4px 10px; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 12px; color: white; background: {{.SeverityColor}};">
        {{.SeverityLabel}}
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>

  <h2 style="margin: 0 0 12px 0; color: #111827;">{{.Title}}</h2>

  {{if .Body}}<p style="color: #374151; line-height: 1.5; white-space: pre-line;">{{.Body}}</p>{{end}}

  {{if .OpenURL}}
  <p style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
    <a href="{{.OpenURL}}"
       style="background: #2563eb; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 16px;">
      Открыть в RepricerX
    </a>
  </p>
  {{end}}

  <hr style="margin-top: 40px; border: none; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">
  <p style="color: #6b7280; font-size: 12px;">
    RepricerX — сервис управления ценами на маркетплейсах.
    {{if .PreferencesURL}}
    Настроить уведомления: <a href="{{.PreferencesURL}}" style="color: #6b7280;">в личном кабинете</a>.
    {{end}}
  </p>
</body>
</html>
